# Educational App Design

## 1. Classroom Mode
- Notes sharing
- Group discussions
- Quizzes
- Term reminders
-Motivational Prompts

## 2. Story Teller/Explainer Mode
- Narration with character voices
- Interactive storytelling
- In-story quizzes

## 3. Teaching Mode
- Teacher tools
- Feedback system
-Points & Badges for Completing Lessons
-Mini Challenges

## 4. Personal Development Mode
- Aptitude & logical reasoning
- Ethics & values


## Additional Global Features
- Gamification
- Progress tracking
- Notifications
- Central dashboard
- Rating\suggestions
